about.summary: A C library that may be linked into a C/C++ program to produce symbolic backtraces

name: backtrace
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "20200511" %}

package:
    name: backtrace
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    url: https://github.com/ianlancetaylor/libbacktrace/archive/14465a957475927900d3483db822b8222e17a196.zip
    sha256: 1f9a46461717176677ef6693e69045f4001cf8f3fdc25ac632011e45e3b4fa04

build:
    number: 0
    skip: true  # [win]

requirements:
    build:
        - {{ compiler('c') }}
    host:
        - zlib

test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libbacktrace.a
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libbacktrace.so     # [linux]
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libbacktrace.dylib  # [osx]
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/include/backtrace.h

about:
    home: https://github.com/ianlancetaylor/libbacktrace
    license: BSD-3-Clause
    summary: A C library that may be linked into a C/C++ program to produce symbolic backtraces
    license_file: LICENSE

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - bluescarni
